<s> Actually, SAX is a little more complicated -- the application has two options for each external entity reference: 1) ask the parser to resolve it; or 2) provide an alternative resolution (including possibly an empty stream).  </s>
<s> More generally, entity references should be invisible to production processes (such as those targeted by SAX), but they will, of course, matter to authoring tools.  </s>
